Dialogs.Dialog: Have you been emailing less often lately？
Why haven't you been emailing me much lately？
Are you trying to say that Rinko is lying？
Hey, can I ask you something...？
You haven't e-mailed me much lately. Why is that？
You think...？ I didn't mean it that way.
I wondered if it means you don't think much about Rinko.
I feel like we're kissing less and less.
You want me to kiss you？
Idiot！ That's not what I meant.
(Maybe I didn't express my love enough...)
You haven't been kissing much lately. What do you mean？
What does that mean？ ...The deeper meaning is...
What's the matter, you look gloomy？
Yeah. You haven't kissed me lately, so I was wondering why.
Don't worry about it. It's not like we're fighting or anything.
There is. Why have you been skipping dates lately？
I'm probably looking forward to it, and I'm sad. Do you understand？
(Hmm, I guess I made her angry...)
Why do you skip out on dates？ You've been doing that a lot lately.
Don't play dumb！ It's been pretty rough...
Yeah... You've been missing a lot of dates, so I was just curious.
It's not like you don't want to date Rinko anymore, right？
Why did you leave Rinko alone on our last date？ I don't like that kind of thing.
You can't fake it. Geez... stop doing that, okay？
You left Rinko alone on our last date. I hate that kind of thing.
(She's a little bit mad at me...)
Rinko is mad at you. Because she was left alone on our last date.
(She seems to be still hurt about that...)
Not that I mind, but... can I ask you one question？
You see me less often these days... Why is that？
It's not like I'm doing it on purpose...
So you have no choice？ Well... I guess that's fine.
You know... You and Rinko haven't seen much lately.
Yeah, it is. Aren't you lonely？
(I guess we need to meet more often...)
You know... why are we seeing each other less often these days？
You should care, geez. I'm pretty lonely.
(I don't want her to miss me too much.)
What's with the lack of energy...
Who was that girl who just came in？ You guys seemed to be getting along pretty well. If you don't want to tell me, that's fine.
What kind of relationship do you have with that girl you were talking with？
What kind of relationship？ We're just friends.
Hmm. Then... Rinko is just a girlfriend.
Hey... you don't have to tell me if you don't want to.
I'm talking about the girl you were chatting so nicely with...
Oh, earlier？ We were just talking normally, we're just friends.
Really？ Then that's fine, but... I was a little worried.
Hmmm... I think I'll be fine if I sleep all day.
Really？ Don't take it too hard.
Are you worried about me？ You're the one who got it... hehe.
It's not good... I'll be fine after a day's sleep.
I hope so... I wonder if I've given you that cold？
Self-conscious. Well... it's probably your cold.
Do you want to return it to me？
It's not good, but I think I'll be fine if I take a day off for this.
Take it easy and get some rest. That cold, it might have been brought on by me...
Do you think so...？ I might still be happy if it was your cold.
Do you want to pass it to me？
I should have been more careful
Do you want to pass it to me？ Then maybe you'll get better faster.
No, you can't do that. If you catch a cold, it's a hassle to take care of you.
Want to give it back？ Don't hesitate.
You idiot. If you do that, Rinko will have to take care of you.
Wanna pass it on me？ I'll take it back responsibly.
Hehe... I'm happy for you, but that means we can't date any time soon.
Sorry. I wish I had been more careful.
You're worrying too much. Rinko will be fine soon.
I did a really bad thing...
That's enough. All I want is for you to stay healthy and take care of Rinko.
I should have been more careful. I'll reflect on that.
Don't worry so much. Even Rinko should have taken better precautions.
Here, I cut up some apples. Do you want some？
Thanks, you're really thoughtful. And now, let me eat.
Thanks for your visit. I was... quite happy. I feel like I'm going to get well soon.
Good. Well, I'm leaving... but if you have any trouble let me know.
Well, it wasn't much to begin with.
Sorry I couldn't make it to visit you.
That's okay. I probably wouldn't have been able to sleep if you came.
It's just a little cold, and it went away as soon as I got some sleep.
Good to hear... Sorry I couldn't visit you.
It's okay. I don't want you to catch a cold when you come to visit me.
Yeah, I'm fine now！ Sorry for worrying you.
I'm sorry I didn't visit you at a time like this...
That's okay. If you came, I'd be so nervous that I wouldn't be able to relax.
Didn't your cold get better faster than expected？
Yeah, I'm sure I'll be fine. Maybe it's because someone gave me a little bit of a cold.
Yeah, I'm fine. Maybe it healed faster than I thought.
Stupid！ ...How can you say such a thing without shame？
You look like you're feeling all right.
Yeah, I know. I think I'm feeling better ahead of schedule. Is it because of your kiss？
Hey, you look red. Fever？ Yeah right... hehe.
I'm a little lax, but nothing serious.
They say a cold goes away faster if you pass it on to someone else, right？
Shall we give it a try？
How's it going？ You feel bad？
Not really. I'm sure it will go away soon if I take it easy.
Do you want Rinko to take that cold for you？
Don't worry about it so much. If I sleep, I'll be fine.
They say that if you pass a cold on to someone else, it will go away faster, right？ Is that true？
Want to give it a try？
Trying it out, with Rinko？ ...I don't mind.
It's fine. Still that is... you know？
That means... that's what it is, right？ Of course, I don't mind...
You're saying those things again... I don't mind.
I can't help it. Better get well soon, okay？
Of course, it's okay. In return, get well soon, okay？
Yeah, I think it's starting to work.
Honestly... you're looking better. If Rinko goes to bed, you have to make sure she is well taken care of.
Hmm, I think I'm getting better...
There is no way it will work that fast. You'll have to take responsibility when Rinko catches a cold.
If Rinko catches a cold, you'll take care of her, right？
(I don't this really works that fast...)
Yeah, it seems to work this time too.
Honestly... I don't know what you are going to do if Rinko catches a cold.
I will take care of you then.
Okay, I made sure I got it right.
Thanks. It seems to be working.
I'm sure you know what I'm talking about, but please do it for Rinko, too.
Yes. I have to make sure I don't infect you ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko doesn't mind if she's infected. Because... you will be nice to me, right？
Don't. I can't have you come to visit me and catch a cold.
Of course it's a lie. Do you believe it, by any chance？
Hey, I made some porridge, do you want some...？
Thanks for today. Thanks to you, I'm feeling better, ▲小早川＊▲.
Good. I'm leaving now, but call me if you need anything else. Bye-bye
Yeah, I think it was just a little cold. I'm totally fine.
Thank goodness... I'm happy it was not a big deal.
You don't have to worry about that, thank you.
Did you get rid of your cold？
Oh, I'm fine now. You were worried about me？
Well, that's once way to see it.
Thanks, I'm glad to hear that.
I'm glad. If you're not feeling well, I'm going to lose my energy too.
Thanks to you, I'm better ▲小早川＊▲.
Heh, I guess that story wasn't a superstition after all.
Maybe so... More important, didn't you catch a cold, ▲小早川＊▲？
Are you worried about me？ I'm fine, though.
Thanks for your visit. I'm feeling much better.
Good for you. Was that thanks to Rinko or something？
Absolutely yes. I'll ask for your help again.
Thanks for visiting me the other day. As you can see, I'm feeling better.
Good. Maybe... did the kiss work？
Maybe. But, you didn't catch a cold, right, ▲小早川＊▲？
Yeah, Rinko feels fine. If I was sick, you would have nursed me back to health... hehe.
Let's see, how can I say it...
Uh... that, I don't mean to repeat myself.
...Well, that's it. Only once. From Rinko to you.
...What are you getting yourself ready for？
It's just... somehow, are you mad at me？
Then, what I was trying to say...
I just wanted to say I love you...
(Aren't you acting a little different from usual ▲小早川＊▲...？)
That's why I said I wanted to spoil you.
What do you wanted to talk about？
I forgot... it's okay, because I'm done with it.
(So you can also be bold, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Did you get the message that I love you？
Please keep on loving me, a lot, okay？
(You're even more aggressive than usual ▲小早川＊▲...)
